description: For sale: $399,999. One of a kind Outdoor Paradise, in a remote location yet 15 minutes to the Miller Mall in Hermantown Minnesota. This is your chance to own a 3 bedroom, 1 bath Log home on 120 acres! This Log home features an open floor plan, gorgeous knotty pine ascents, a wood burning stove for extra warmth and a 3 car detached garage with a bar and TV access. There is something for every season here;  Hunt year round, (7 deer stands remain on the property),  Snowmobile, 4 wheel , XC Ski , Snowshoe, or fish winter and summer on Round Lake ( 2 boats stored on this remote lake for the new owners)  . Less than 30 minutes to downtown Duluth and 2 hours to the north Mpls/St Paul metro area.                                                    What are you waiting for ?..... escape to Northern Minnesota and all it has to offer and explore from the comfort of a gorgeous warm home.
